        <abstract>
            <p>CD’s pleasure at JDH’s willingness to help Scott find a position in India.</p>
            <p>Naudin underrates contamination of his experiments by insects. Thus CD doubts Naudin’s results on rapidity and universality of reversion in hybrids.</p> 
<p>Wallace’s paper on man [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">4494</hi>] reflects his genius, although CD does not fully agree with it.</p> 
        </abstract>
